### üß© **Description of Change**

#### üèóÔ∏è **Application Architecture & Technical Foundation**

* Converted entire application from JavaScript to **TypeScript** (app.tsx & not app.js) for type safety and better development experience
* Implemented **React Navigation with TypeScript** for type-safe screen transitions and parameter passing
* Set up **proper development environment** using Expo Dev with Android/iOS emulation (not Web) for true React Native functionality
* Created comprehensive **type definitions** for all components, navigation parameters, and data structures
* Implemented **AsyncStorage persistence** with proper error handling and data validation

---

#### üè† **Home Page Implementation**

* Built **clean, functional home screen** with minimal styling as requested
* Added **administrative access button** positioned top-right for menu management
* Implemented **restaurant branding** with shop name and menu title display
* Included **promotional content** area for special offers and announcements
* Created **primary call-to-action button** for seamless navigation to main menu
* Ensured **background image integration** with proper scaling and overlay content

---

#### üçΩÔ∏è **Menu Page Complete Overhaul**

* Implemented **three-column layout** for categories (Starters, Mains, Desserts) with proper spacing
* Added **dynamic category filtering system** with visual active states
* Created **category-based meal counters** showing items per category
* Implemented **price range calculations** for each category display
* Fixed **Add to Cart button positioning** to prevent overflow and ensure proper layout
* Added **professional card designs** with meal images, descriptions, and pricing
* Implemented **real-time cart updates** with proper state management
* Enhanced **empty state displays** with helpful messaging and icons

---

#### üõí **Cart System Enhancement**

* Fixed **cart persistence issues** - items no longer disappear when adding new items
* Implemented **quantity management system** using item IDs instead of array indices
* Added **category-based filtering within cart** (All, Starters, Mains, Desserts)
* Created **comprehensive cart summary** with total items, subtotal, average price, and category breakdowns
* Implemented **real-time total calculations** with proper currency formatting
* Added **item removal confirmation dialogs** to prevent accidental deletions
* Enhanced **cart item displays** with category badges and detailed information
* Fixed **layout overlapping issues** with proper spacing and scroll view implementation

---

#### ‚öôÔ∏è **Menu Management System**

* Built **complete administrative interface** for menu creation and management
* Implemented **category-based meal organization** with visual category selection
* Added **meal limit enforcement** (maximum 2 items per category) with user feedback
* Created **dynamic image assignment system** based on category and position
* Implemented **form validation** for all input fields with clear error messages
* Added **meal removal functionality** with confirmation dialogs
* Enhanced **real-time category counters** showing current/total capacity

---

#### üí≥ **Checkout System Implementation**

* Built **comprehensive checkout form** with delivery information collection
* Implemented **robust form validation** for:
  * Required name field validation
  * Email format validation with regex pattern matching
  * Phone number validation (7-15 digits)
  * Delivery address requirement checking
  * Empty cart prevention
* Added **promo code system** with pre-defined discount codes (DISCOUNT10, WELCOME15, SAVE25)
* Implemented **real-time discount calculations** and application feedback
* Created **detailed order summary** with itemized breakdown and totals
* Added **order confirmation system** with success messaging and navigation
* Implemented **security assurance displays** for user confidence

---

#### üé® **UI/UX & Design Transformation**

* Implemented **Cappuccino Cream Color Theme** throughout application:
  * Cream backgrounds with coffee brown accents
  * Caramel highlights for buttons and important elements
  * Success colors for positive feedback
  * Professional white text with shadows for readability
* Created **consistent card-based layouts** with proper shadows and borders
* Added **professional typography hierarchy** with clear information organization
* Implemented **responsive design** using Dimensions API for proper screen adaptation
* Enhanced **touch target sizes** and spacing for mobile usability
* Added **visual feedback** for all interactive elements (buttons, filters, inputs)
* Implemented **loading states** and empty state handling throughout application

---

#### üêõ **Critical Bug Fixes & Optimizations**

* Fixed **category counting system** - discovered and resolved undefined category assignments
* Resolved **cart reset logic** in App.tsx for proper session management
* Fixed **color scheme consistency** by adding missing COLORS.success definition
* Corrected **layout overflow issues** with proper button positioning and spacing
* Enhanced **AsyncStorage error handling** with proper fallback mechanisms
* Improved **state management** with functional updates to prevent stale state
* Optimized **re-render performance** with proper dependency arrays and conditional rendering

---

#### üìö **Academic Documentation & Code Quality**

